## Code locations

- **CLI UI**: `packages/cli/src/pages` (e.g., [packages/cli/src/pages/_app.tsx](mdc:packages/cli/src/pages/_app.tsx))
- **Core lib**: `packages/core/src` (e.g., [packages/core/src/index.ts](mdc:packages/core/src/index.ts))
- **Web (site/docs)**: `packages/web/pages` and `packages/web/components` (e.g., [packages/web/pages/_app.tsx](mdc:packages/web/pages/_app.tsx))

## Tests and e2e

- **Unit/Jest**: `packages/*/src/**/__test__/**` (e.g., [packages/core/src/__test__/index.test.tsx](mdc:packages/core/src/__test__/index.test.tsx))
- **Cypress (CLI)**: `packages/cli/cypress` (e.g., [packages/cli/cypress/e2e/index.cy.js](mdc:packages/cli/cypress/e2e/index.cy.js))
- **E2E harness**: `e2e/mailing_tests/cypress` (e.g., [e2e/mailing_tests/cypress/e2e/index.cy.js](mdc:e2e/mailing_tests/cypress/e2e/index.cy.js))

